mindmap
  root((AI Influencer Video))
    The Problem
      Static images don't build connection
      Frozen characters get scrolled past
      Consistency alone isn't enough
    The Solution
      Face-swap onto stock footage
      Map synthetic face to real movement
      Cloud GPU processing
        Free tier available
        ~1 min per second of video
    Quality Reality
      Not perfect at 100% zoom
      Phone displays forgive imperfections
      Sufficient for social content
    What It Unlocks
      Movement creates presence
      Dancing, talking, gesturing
      Stops thumbs mid-scroll
      Builds parasocial connection
    Content Possibilities
      Stock footage libraries
        Dance videos
        Lifestyle clips
        Conversational footage
      One face, infinite videos